title: American Horror Story Season 7 Theme reveal reaction
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Lol I am so interested in the concept of cults so I've been wanting this theme to happen for a while. Sorry you're not excited though!

i honestly love that it's called cult maybe somehow they're trying to bring twisty back to life or something? i heard it's supposed to connect to every season this season i'm really excited for this one! but i respect you're opinion:)
Cults are very interesting and I love that they have chosen this one. I knew that they would choose it eventually because cults are very mysterious and I'd love to see their take on this new theme.
